developers to get their compilers to run faster.

00:53:13.100 --> 00:53:15.480
PHP's got Xen and they've got stuff.

00:53:15.480 --> 00:53:16.940
I mean, the list goes on.

00:53:16.940 --> 00:53:17.760
Java's got Oracle.

00:53:17.760 --> 00:53:23.300
I mean, we are the only one at that level that is completely run by a group of volunteers.

00:53:23.300 --> 00:53:25.700
Even Rust, right, is backed by Mozilla.

00:53:25.700 --> 00:53:28.040
And that's very much a community-run project.

