01:00:28.520 --> 01:00:33.980
And basically the way to think about it, you can go from positional-only to positional-only to positional-only to keyword-only.

01:00:33.980 --> 01:00:36.920
And actually the syntax actually works with that mnemonic.

01:00:36.920 --> 01:00:41.860
In case you haven't seen it, basically what happens is you have your parameters.

01:00:41.860 --> 01:00:44.440
